-- TNK-BP Said to Sell July ESPO to Trafigura at $4-$4.30 Premium
-- B y   R a m s e y   A l - R i k a b i
-- 2012-06-13T05:32:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-13/tnk-bp-said-to-sell-july-espo-to-trafigura-at-4-4-30-premium.html
TNK-BP, the Russian oil producer
part-owned by  BP Plc (BP/) , sold a cargo of East Siberia Pacific Ocean
crude loading in July to Trafigura Beheer BV, said four traders
who participate in the market, declining to be identified
because the information is confidential.  Trafigura paid a premium of $4 to $4.30 a barrel above the
benchmark price of Dubai oil, according to the traders.  Details of the deal are as follows:  To contact the reporter on this story:
